---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — dord.racing"
  description="Privacy policy for dord.racing. Analytics cookies (GA4) require consent. Affiliate links may set third-party cookies."
  canonicalUrl="https://dord.racing/legal/privacy"
>
  <header>
    <div class="header--left">
      <div class="header--dept">The Department of Racing Drivers</div>
      <h1>dord.racing</h1>
      <div class="meta">LEGAL — PRIVACY POLICY</div>
      <Nav activePage="calendar" />
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="main-content" class="legal-page">
    <a href={`${base}/`} class="back-link">← Back to Calendar</a>

    <div class="legal-body">

      <p class="legal-date">Last updated: July 10, 2026 — fonts are now self-hosted; no third-party font requests</p>

      <h2>1. Who we are</h2>
      <p>dord.racing is operated by Yann Durandet, based in France. For privacy-related questions, contact us at <a class="js-mailto" data-u="durandet.yann.pro" data-d="gmail.com" data-show></a>. As the site is operated from France, it is subject to the EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).</p>

      <h2>2. Data we collect</h2>
      <p>dord.racing does not collect, store, or process any personal data directly. There is no account system, no contact form, and no newsletter.</p>
      <p>Your calendar filter preferences (series, region, and category selections) are saved to your browser's <strong>local storage</strong> under the key <code>motorsportFilters</code>. Local storage is a browser-side mechanism — this data is stored only on your device, is never transmitted to any server, and is not accessible to us. You can clear it at any time by clearing your browser's site data for dord.racing.</p>

      <h2>3. Analytics cookies (Google Analytics 4)</h2>
      <p>With your consent, we use Google Analytics 4 (GA4) to understand how visitors find and use the site — for example, which series pages are most popular and how visitors arrive (search, social, direct). GA4 sets first-party cookies on your device. The data collected is aggregated and used only to improve the site; we do not use it to identify individuals.</p>
      <p>GA4 is only loaded after you click <strong>Accept</strong> in the cookie consent banner shown on your first visit. If you click Decline, no analytics script is loaded and no analytics cookies are set. Your preference is stored in a <code>cookie_consent</code> cookie (1-year expiry) so the banner does not reappear on subsequent visits. You can withdraw consent at any time by clearing your cookies — the banner will reappear on your next visit.</p>
      <p>When GA4 is active, data is processed by Google LLC in accordance with <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Privacy Policy</a>. You can also opt out at any time using the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.</p>

      <h2>4. Affiliate links and third-party cookies</h2>
      <p>Some links on this site are affiliate links. When you click an affiliate link, you are redirected to a third-party platform (such as a ticketing partner or streaming service). These platforms may set their own cookies on your device in order to track referrals and attribute purchases to us.</p>
      <p>These cookies are set by third parties, not by dord.racing. We have no control over them. The data collected by affiliate platforms is governed by their own privacy policies. We encourage you to review those policies before making a purchase.</p>
      <p>Affiliate cookies typically persist for 7 to 30 days depending on the programme. They are used solely to determine whether a purchase resulted from a click on our site, so that we can receive the applicable commission.</p>

      <h2>5. Legal basis for processing (GDPR)</h2>
      <p>Analytics cookies (GA4) are loaded only on the basis of your explicit consent (GDPR Art. 6(1)(a)). Affiliate tracking cookies set by third-party platforms when you click a link fall under the legitimate interests of those platforms (GDPR Art. 6(1)(f)); their data processing is governed by their own policies.</p>

      <h2>6. Cloudflare Pages hosting</h2>
      <p>This site is hosted on Cloudflare Pages (a service of Cloudflare, Inc.). Cloudflare may collect basic server access logs (IP address, browser type, referring URL, country) as part of normal hosting and DDoS-protection operations. This is governed by <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cloudflare's Privacy Policy</a>. dord.racing does not have access to these logs.</p>

      <h2>7. Fonts</h2>
      <p>Fonts (Orbitron, Roboto Mono, Inter) are self-hosted on dord.racing. No request is made to Google Fonts or any third-party font CDN, so no IP address or browser data is transmitted to Google as a result of loading this site's typography.</p>

      <h2>8. Your rights (GDPR)</h2>
      <p>If you are located in the EU or UK, you have rights under the GDPR including the right to access, rectify, or erase personal data held about you. As dord.racing holds no personal data itself, there is nothing to access or delete on our end. For data held by third-party platforms or GitHub, please contact those services directly. To withdraw analytics consent, clear your cookies and decline on your next visit.</p>

      <h2>9. Changes</h2>
      <p>This policy may be updated as we add new features. Material changes will be reflected in the "Last updated" date above.</p>

      <h2>10. Contact</h2>
      <p>Privacy questions: <a class="js-mailto" data-u="durandet.yann.pro" data-d="gmail.com" data-show></a></p>

    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem 4rem;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: #8a9aaa;
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }
  .back-link:hover { color: #aaa; }

  .legal-body {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    color: #9aa;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .legal-date {
    font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #7a8fa0;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .legal-body h2 {
    font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    color: #6a9ab0;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 2rem 0 0.6rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.4rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #1a2530;
  }

  .legal-body p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.9rem;
    color: #8a9aaa;
  }

  .legal-body a {
    color: #5a8fa8;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .legal-body a:hover { color: #aad; text-decoration: underline; }
</style>
